  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/kernel\/ioaudiodevice\/familymanagepower\ncrawled: 2025-12-11T16:53:54Z\n---\n\n# familyManagePower\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nbool familyManagePower;\n```\n\n## Overview\n\nSet to true if the family is supposed to manage power - this is the default state. It can be changed early in the initialization process with a call to setFamilyManagePower().\n\n## Instance Variables\n\n- **workLoop**\n- **timerEventSource**\n- **timerEvents**: The set of timer events in use by the device.\n- **pendingPowerState**\n- **numRunningAudioEngines**\n- **minimumInterval**\n- **duringStartup**\n- **currentPowerState**\n- **commandGate**\n- **audioPorts**\n- **audioEngines**\n- **asyncPowerStateChangeInProgress**\n\n",
